{"data":[{"date":"09:04 26/07","title":"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay (26/7/2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-2672018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>B\u1ecb anh em nh\u00e0 Neville cho r\u1eb1ng thi\u1ebfu chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, l\u00e0 \u201cn\u1ed7i \u00f4 nh\u1ee5c\u201d c\u1ee7a Stoke, nh\u01b0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Shaqiri kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch c\u1ee7a huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nShaqiri ph\u1edbt l\u1edd ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m nay, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 \u0111\u00e3 gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 13 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, kh\u00e1 r\u1ebb cho t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a anh. S\u1edf d\u0129 c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y, b\u1edfi Stoke \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng v\u00e0 m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Shaqiri \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3m xu\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. M\u1ed9t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 qu\u00e1 h\u1eddi, m\u00e0 theo Jurgen Klopp chia s\u1ebb l\u00e0 \u00f4ng ch\u1eb3ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i suy ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, anh em nh\u00e0 Neville l\u1ea1i l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng nghi ng\u1edd s\u1ef1 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a Shaqiri trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i \u1edf Stoke City, khi cho r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn h\u1ebft kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng \u0111\u1ec3 ra \u0111i cho d\u1ec5.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e1p l\u1eddi, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 b\u00ecnh th\u1ea3n: &ldquo;H\u1ecd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Man United &ndash; CLB ch\u1eb3ng \u01b0a g\u00ec Liverpool. T\u00f4i hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi y\u00eau th\u00edch, v\u00e0 c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng \u01b0a. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n t\u1ed1n th\u1eddi gian b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u00e0 t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Shaqiri kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch c\u1ee7a huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i M.U\" title=\"Liverpool mua Shaqiri t\u1eeb Stoke v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 13,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/14/shaqiri-buong-loi-dap-tra-khi-bi-huyen-thoai-mu-chui-thang-mat.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Shaqiri kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch c\u1ee7a huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i M.U</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u 3 n\u0103m t\u1ea1i Premier League v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o, t\u00f4i c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u. Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, v\u00ec v\u1eady t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 ai. M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng t\u00f4i l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hay nh\u1ea5t Stoke City m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc. L\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec c\u1ea3.&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, sau khi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Xherdan Shaqiri kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch, anh c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi Liverpool, v\u1ec1 \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y Jurgen Klopp v\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992 mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u danh hi\u1ec7u, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 Champions League.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-liverpool-21-man-city-icc-2018-326-192055.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/video-tong-hop-liverpool-21-man-city-icc-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-liverpool-21-man-city-icc-2018-326-192055.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Liverpool 2-1 Man City (ICC 2018)</span><br>\r\nS\u1ef1 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Mohamed Salah sau khi v\u00e0o s\u00e2n trong hi\u1ec7p 2 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf th\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea1nh tranh quen thu\u1ed9c t\u1ea1i Premier League trong tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tan-binh-liverpool-ha-muc-tieu-vo-dich-champions-league-172-192043.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/tan-binh-liverpool-ha-muc-tieu-vo-dich-champions-league.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tan-binh-liverpool-ha-muc-tieu-vo-dich-champions-league-172-192043.html\">T\u00e2n binh Liverpool h\u1ea1 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Xherdan Shaqiri m\u1ea1nh d\u1ea1n h\u1ea1 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Anfield trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1649","checkdouble":"192051"},{"date":"09:41 26/07","title":"Sao M.U c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi c\u00f3 HLV m\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/sao-mu-cam-thay-hanh-phuc-khi-co-hlv-moi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Man United \u2013 Andreas Pereira chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Michael Carrick v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi l\u1ebd r\u1ea5t t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nPereira vui m\u1eebng khi c\u00f3 th\u1ea7y m\u1edbi<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil, Andreas Pereira \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1ea1i La Liga, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi quay v\u1ec1 Man United v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 v\u00e0 \u0111ang c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i tham gia tour du \u0111\u1ea5u. Anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i c\u1ea3 2 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1eeba qua v\u1edbi vai tr\u00f2 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m, v\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi Jose Mourinho.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eebng xem Carrick l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n anh \u0111\u00e1ng ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 \u1edf Man United, Pereira \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u t\u1eeb ti\u1ec1n b\u1ed1i, v\u00e0 cho bi\u1ebft r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng khi Carrick tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd HLV sau khi gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7. Sao tr\u1ebb Brazil h\u1ebft l\u1eddi ca ng\u1ee3i:<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Anh \u1ea5y \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. Carrick lu\u00f4n b\u1ea3o t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m g\u00ec v\u00e0 gi\u00fap t\u00f4i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n. N\u1ebfu t\u00f4i l\u00e0m sai hay \u0111\u00fang, anh \u1ea5y c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chia s\u1ebb. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi b\u1edfi anh \u1ea5y c\u0169ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Andreas Pereira chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Michael Carrick \" title=\"Pereira\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/sao-mu-cam-thay-hanh-phuc-khi-co-hlv-moi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Andreas Pereira chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Michael Carrick&nbsp;</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n&ldquo;R\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. V\u00e0 khi anh \u1ea5y n\u00f3i v\u1edbi b\u1ea1n m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3, n\u00f3 r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp thu. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t may m\u1eafn khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a Carrick&rdquo; &ndash; Andreas Pereira chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00e0n anh.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn ra m\u1eaft M.U v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 8/2014, \u0111\u1ebfn nay sao tr\u1ebb Brazil ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 12 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. Anh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean b\u1ecb g\u1eedi \u0111i cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n nh\u01b0ng l\u00fac n\u00e0y, \u0111\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh v\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, \u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong suy ngh\u0129 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u00e0m t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ec3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y. T\u00f4i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1eeb khi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u, nh\u01b0ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ch\u01a1i \u1edf b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0o mi\u1ec5n l\u00e0 HLV y\u00eau c\u1ea7u.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;L\u00fac n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 6, nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i s\u1ed1 8. T\u00f4i \u0111ang h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi t\u1eeb Carrick v\u00e0 HLV Mourinho. H\u1ecd \u0111ang gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0 t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t&rdquo; &ndash; Andreas Pereira chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Michael Carrick v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cuc-nong-mourinho-noi-dien-muon-tong-khu-martial-cang-nhanh-cang-tot-172-192038.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/14/cuc-nong-mourinho-noi-dien-muon-tong-khu-martial-cang-nhanh-cang-tot.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cuc-nong-mourinho-noi-dien-muon-tong-khu-martial-cang-nhanh-cang-tot-172-192038.html\">C\u1ef0C N\u00d3NG: Mourinho n\u1ed5i \u0111i\u00ean, mu\u1ed1n t\u1ed1ng kh\u1ee9 Martial c\u00e0ng nhanh c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t</span><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng MU b\u00e1n Anthony Martial l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao, HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111ang r\u1ea5t t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y r\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i b\u1ea3n doanh c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng b\u1ea1n g\u00e1i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00f3n c\u1eadu...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/mu-vs-ac-milan-tran-dau-icc-2018-ngay-hom-nay-372-192027.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/mu-vs-ac-milan-tran-dau-icc-2018-ngay-hom-nay.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/mu-vs-ac-milan-tran-dau-icc-2018-ngay-hom-nay-372-192027.html\">TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP MU vs AC Milan 10h00 ng\u00e0y 26/7 (ICC 2018)</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp MU vs AC Milan: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Manchester United vs AC Milan gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1648","checkdouble":"192053"},{"date":"10:50 26/07","title":"Ibrahimovic c\u00fai \u0111\u1ea7u xin l\u1ed7i NHM MU v\u00e0 l\u00fd do b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/6/10/ibrahimovic-cui-dau-xin-loi-nhm-mu-va-ly-do-bat-ngo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n nu\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfc v\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Old Trafford v\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh s\u1edbm h\u01a1n trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Zlatan Ibrahimovic t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng ngay trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Man Utd v\u1edbi 28 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n mang v\u1ec1 c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap danh hi\u1ec7u Europa League v\u00e0 League Cup.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian \u1edf Old Trafford \u0111\u1eb9p \u0111\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng ng\u1eafn ng\u1ee7i bi\u1ebft bao khi v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 bu\u1ed9c l\u00f2ng ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i \u1edf n\u0103m th\u1ee9 hai trong s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">H\u01a1n th\u1ebf n\u1eefa \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 35-36 x\u1ebf b\u00f3ng s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta c\u0169ng kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n n\u1eefa \u1edf Zlatan, khi \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p d\u00f9 c\u00f3 c\u00f2n v\u1eb9n nguy\u00ean c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p y\u1ebfu \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a anh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ibra xin l\u1ed7i MU v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 s\u1edbm h\u01a1n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ibra xin l\u1ed7i MU v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 s\u1edbm h\u01a1n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/6/10/ibrahimovic-cui-dau-xin-loi-nhm-mu-va-ly-do-bat-ngo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ibra xin l\u1ed7i MU v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 s\u1edbm h\u01a1n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u0169ng ch\u00ednh v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y l\u1ea1i c\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn Ibra c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ed1i h\u1eadn nh\u01b0 Robin Van Persie thu\u1edf n\u00e0o, r\u1eb1ng anh \u0111\u00e3 \u201cv\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 h\u01a1i mu\u1ed9n\u201d. L\u1eddi xin l\u1ed7i ch\u00e2n th\u00e0nh v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 th\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m ph\u1ea7n ki\u00eau h\u00e3nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00f4i sao B\u1eafc \u00c2u g\u1eedi t\u1edbi c\u00e1c C\u0110V Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i xin l\u1ed7i v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1ea5y l\u00e0m ti\u1ebfc cho fan Man Utd. N\u1ebfu h\u1ecd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y t\u00f4i s\u1edbm h\u01a1n v\u00e0 tr\u1ebb h\u01a1n, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t con s\u01b0 t\u1eed r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c.\u201d - Ibra xin l\u1ed7i MU<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, Premier League s\u1ebd b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t trong m\u1ed1i nguy l\u1edbn h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u, khi t\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u0103n t\u01b0\u01a1i nu\u1ed1t s\u1ed1ng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y v\u00e0o b\u1eefa s\u00e1ng thay v\u00ec d\u00f9ng cho bu\u1ed5i tr\u01b0a. D\u00f9 sao th\u00ec t\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00e0 chinh ph\u1ee5c n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh r\u1ed3i. H\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n t\u00f4i, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng v\u00e0 ra \u0111i.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f2n c\u1ea7n th\u00eam r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 chia s\u1ebb c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, nh\u01b0ng h\u00e3y c\u1ee9 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi c\u1ea3m \u01a1n bao la \u0111i. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n d\u00e0nh n\u00f3 cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng ai li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn Man Utd, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t c\u00e1c C\u0110V, v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m cho t\u00f4i. Hy v\u1ecdng h\u1ecd c\u0169ng s\u1ebd h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac nh\u01b0 t\u00f4i.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 l\u00e2u nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 cho m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 khi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c nhau, may m\u1eafn h\u01a1n n\u1eefa v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 h\u1ebft l\u00f2ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3, gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 C\u0110V.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cMan Utd s\u1ebd m\u00e3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u1ea3nh gh\u00e9p \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t n\u1ee5 c\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u00ean m\u00f4i. Ch\u00fac cho CLB m\u1ecdi s\u1ef1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1647","checkdouble":"192054"},{"date":"11:05 26/07","title":"Shaqiri bu\u00f4ng l\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 khi b\u1ecb huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i M.U ch\u1eedi th\u1eb3ng m\u1eb7t","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/shaqiri-buong-loi-dap-tra-khi-bi-huyen-thoai-mu-chui-thang-mat.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>B\u1ecb anh em nh\u00e0 Neville cho r\u1eb1ng thi\u1ebfu chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, l\u00e0 \u201cn\u1ed7i \u00f4 nh\u1ee5c\u201d c\u1ee7a Stoke, nh\u01b0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Shaqiri kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch c\u1ee7a huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nShaqiri ph\u1edbt l\u1edd ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m nay, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 \u0111\u00e3 gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 13 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, kh\u00e1 r\u1ebb cho t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a anh. S\u1edf d\u0129 c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y, b\u1edfi Stoke \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng v\u00e0 m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Shaqiri \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3m xu\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. M\u1ed9t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 qu\u00e1 h\u1eddi, m\u00e0 theo Jurgen Klopp chia s\u1ebb l\u00e0 \u00f4ng ch\u1eb3ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i suy ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, anh em nh\u00e0 Neville l\u1ea1i l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng nghi ng\u1edd s\u1ef1 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a Shaqiri trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i \u1edf Stoke City, khi cho r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn h\u1ebft kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng \u0111\u1ec3 ra \u0111i cho d\u1ec5.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e1p l\u1eddi, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 b\u00ecnh th\u1ea3n: &ldquo;H\u1ecd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Man United &ndash; CLB ch\u1eb3ng \u01b0a g\u00ec Liverpool. T\u00f4i hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi y\u00eau th\u00edch, v\u00e0 c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng \u01b0a. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n t\u1ed1n th\u1eddi gian b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u00e0 t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Shaqiri kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch c\u1ee7a huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i M.U\" title=\"Liverpool mua Shaqiri t\u1eeb Stoke v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 13,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/14/shaqiri-buong-loi-dap-tra-khi-bi-huyen-thoai-mu-chui-thang-mat.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Shaqiri kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch c\u1ee7a huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i M.U</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u 3 n\u0103m t\u1ea1i Premier League v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o, t\u00f4i c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u. Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, v\u00ec v\u1eady t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 ai. M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng t\u00f4i l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hay nh\u1ea5t Stoke City m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc. L\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec c\u1ea3.&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, sau khi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Xherdan Shaqiri kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch, anh c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi Liverpool, v\u1ec1 \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y Jurgen Klopp v\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992 mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u danh hi\u1ec7u, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 Champions League.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-liverpool-21-man-city-icc-2018-326-192055.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/video-tong-hop-liverpool-21-man-city-icc-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-liverpool-21-man-city-icc-2018-326-192055.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Liverpool 2-1 Man City (ICC 2018)</span><br>\r\nS\u1ef1 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Mohamed Salah sau khi v\u00e0o s\u00e2n trong hi\u1ec7p 2 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf th\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea1nh tranh quen thu\u1ed9c t\u1ea1i Premier League trong tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tan-binh-liverpool-ha-muc-tieu-vo-dich-champions-league-172-192043.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/tan-binh-liverpool-ha-muc-tieu-vo-dich-champions-league.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tan-binh-liverpool-ha-muc-tieu-vo-dich-champions-league-172-192043.html\">T\u00e2n binh Liverpool h\u1ea1 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Xherdan Shaqiri m\u1ea1nh d\u1ea1n h\u1ea1 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Anfield trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1646","checkdouble":"192056"},{"date":"10:21 26/07","title":"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Man City 1-2 Liverpool: D\u00f9 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o, Kop v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu King","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/du-am-man-city-12-liverpool-du-the-nao-kop-van-khong-the-thieu-king.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Liverpool \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh tay v\u00e0o chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean, h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu \u0111i \u201cVua Ai C\u1eadp\u201d Mohamed Salah. D\u01b0 \u00e2m Man City 1-2 Liverpool trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u International Champions Cup ch\u1ec9 ra \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>M\u1ed9t Liverpool r\u1eddi r\u1ea1c trong hi\u1ec7p 1</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLiverpool b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Man City trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup v\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 Andrew Robertson v\u00e0 Virgil van Dijk \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 c\u00f3 su\u1ea5t c\u1ee9ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i 1. C\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd ho\u1eb7c l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb, ho\u1eb7c l\u00e0 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng James Milner, Georginio Wijnaldum hay Adam Lallana \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0m kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 li\u00ean k\u1ebft c\u00e1c tuy\u1ebfn. H\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t d\u00f9 tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa Man City ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb nh\u01b0 Phil Foden hay Olek Zinchenko.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Man City 1-2 Liverpool Kop v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu King h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Man City 1-2 Liverpool Kop v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu King h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/Du-am-Man-City-1-2-Liverpool-Kop-van-khong-the-thieu-King-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Man City l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt Liverpool trong hi\u1ec7p 1</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Liverpool ph\u1ea3i c\u0103ng m\u00ecnh l\u00ean \u0111u\u1ed5i theo nh\u1eefng pha ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a Man City. Ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh 2 ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb Riyad Mahrez song \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Manchester v\u1eabn th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n r\u00f5 \u00fd \u0111\u1ed3 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a HLV Pep Guardiola. V\u1eabn l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng pha \u0111\u1eadp nh\u1ea3 nh\u1ecbp nh\u00e0ng \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa mang \u0111\u1eadm d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n Tiki-Taka.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu trung phong Lukas Nmecha hay ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Zinchenko nh\u1ea1y b\u00e9n h\u01a1n, Man City \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc. \u1ede ph\u00eda b\u00ean kia, nh\u1eefng pha l\u00ean b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n. H\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 kh\u00e2u t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t l\u1ed9m c\u1ed9m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ef1 b\u1ebf t\u1eafc c\u1ee7a Liverpool th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n qua vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1eafm Daniel Sturridge kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0o trong c\u1ea3 hi\u1ec7p 1. T\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Curtis Jones ch\u01a1i c\u00f3 n\u00e9t nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i chung v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u00e0n anh b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV guardiola\" title=\"HLV guardiola\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/HLV-guardiola.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00dd \u0111\u1ed3 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a HLV Guardiola \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n r\u00f5</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nKh\u1edfi s\u1eafc khi c\u00f3 Salah</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a Mohamed Salah v\u1edbi Liverpool l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i nhi\u1ec1u. Con s\u1ed1 32 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ed9ng 10 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o t\u1ea1i Premier League m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Ai C\u1eadp. Ch\u1ec9 khi anh g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt HLV Jurgen Klopp \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1t t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9 nguy hi\u1ec3m cao nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u01b0 \u00e2m Man City 1-2 Liverpool c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ngo\u1ea1i l\u1ec7. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Salah v\u00e0o s\u00e2n, Liverpool \u0111ang b\u1ecb d\u1eabn 1-0. Ph\u00fat 57, Leroy Sane b\u1ee9t \u0111i r\u1ea5t nhanh sau \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Bernardo v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00e9o g\u00f3c m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho Man City.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Salah danh dau ghi ban\" title=\"Salah danh dau ghi ban\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/Salah-danh-dau-ghi-ban.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Salah \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u ghi b\u00e0n ch\u1ec9 30 gi\u00e2y sau khi v\u00e0o s\u00e2n</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u1ed9i 1 c\u1ee7a Man City \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p Liverpool. B\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a The Kop tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng g\u00ec kh\u00e1c ngo\u00e0i s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Salah v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Mane. C\u00f3 h\u1ecd, \u00e1p l\u1ef1c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Liverpool \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1eadt v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda khung th\u00e0nh Man City.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u00ednh Mane v\u00e0 Salah l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t ghi 2 b\u00e0n c\u00e1c ph\u00fat 63 v\u00e0 90+4 gi\u00fap Liverpool ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 r\u00f5 vai tr\u00f2 to l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/liverpool-vs-man-city-tran-dau-giai-icc-2018-372-192022.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/liverpool-vs-man-city-tran-dau-giai-icc-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/liverpool-vs-man-city-tran-dau-giai-icc-2018-372-192022.html\">Liverpool 2-1 Man City (KT): Song s\u00e1t Salah vs Mane gi\u00fap The Kop th\u1eafng k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh Man xanh</span><br>\r\n<span>S\u1ef1 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Mohamed Salah sau khi v\u00e0o s\u00e2n trong hi\u1ec7p 2 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf th\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea1nh tranh quen thu\u1ed9c t\u1ea1i Premier League trong tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi c\u00f3 Mane v\u00e0 Salah tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, Liverpool gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc l\u00f2 xo \u0111\u1ea7y l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb d\u1ed3n \u00e9p nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c \u00e1p s\u00e1t khung th\u00e0nh b\u00ean kia ch\u1ec9 trong m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian ng\u1eafn. M\u1ea5u ch\u1ed1t n\u1eb1m \u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ee9t t\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a hai m\u0169i c\u00f4ng ch\u00e2u Phi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 Salah.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0 m\u1ecdi khi, Salah v\u1eabn l\u00e0 c\u1ee5c nam ch\u00e2m h\u00fat t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 s\u1ef1 ch\u00fa \u00fd c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Man City. Anh c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1eafc s\u1ea3o ghi b\u00e0n. Ch\u1ec9 kho\u1ea3ng 30 gi\u00e2y sau khi v\u00e0o s\u00e2n, &ldquo;Vua Ai C\u1eadp&rdquo; \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m tung l\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Joe Hart sau c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Salah ghi ban cho Liverpool\" title=\"Salah ghi ban cho Liverpool\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/Salah-ghi-ban-cho-Liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>D\u01b0 \u00e2m Man City 1-2 Liverpool n\u00f3i l\u00ean t\u1ea7m quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Salah</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau \u0111\u00f3, s\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khung th\u00e0nh Man City li\u00ean t\u1ee5c n\u1ed5i l\u00ean xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb c\u00e1i ch\u00e2n tr\u00e1i phi th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a Salah. N\u1ebfu may m\u1eafn h\u01a1n, Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi Premier League m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t hat-trick. Anh 1 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng tr\u00fang x\u00e0 ngang v\u00e0 1 l\u1ea7n b\u1ecb ph\u00e1 ra ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nXen k\u1ebd trong \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 v\u00f4 s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng pha \u0111i b\u00f3ng l\u1eaft l\u00e9o l\u00e0m kh\u1ed5 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Man City c\u1ee7a Salah. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, c\u00f3 s\u1ed1 11 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, Liverpool m\u1edbi th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh. H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i chi 163 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1eb1m chinh ph\u1ee5c c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u. Nh\u01b0ng d\u00f9 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o, phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Salah v\u1eabn quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u00e0nh b\u1ea1i h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng n\u00f3i ri\u00eang v\u00e0 to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i Liverpool n\u00f3i chung.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem l\u1ea1i video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Liverpool 2-1 man city (ICC 2018):</strong>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/26/Liverpool-2-1-Man-city.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Liverpool tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/goc-liverpool-qua-roi-thoi-dung-dao-dau-voi-cac-xa-thu-172-191980.html\">G\u00f3c Liverpool: Qua r\u1ed3i th\u1eddi d\u00f9ng dao \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi c\u00e1c x\u1ea1 th\u1ee7</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/goc-nhin-sturridge-o-lai-liverpool-la-dieu-tot-cho-tat-ca-172-191904.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Sturridge \u1edf l\u1ea1i Liverpool l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/4-dieu-xay-ra-sau-khi-liverpool-chieu-mo-alisson-becker-172-191685.html\">4 \u0111i\u1ec1u x\u1ea3y ra sau khi Liverpool chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Alisson Becker</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-chieu-mo-thu-mon-alisson-dau-roi-loi-mia-mai-172-191662.html\">Liverpool bi\u1ebfn Alisson th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi: \u0110\u00e2u r\u1ed3i l\u1eddi m\u1ec9a mai?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-chieu-mo-alisson-ho-da-co-de-gea-cua-rieng-minh-172-191659.html\">Liverpool chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Alisson: H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 De Gea c\u1ee7a ri\u00eang m\u00ecnh!</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1645","checkdouble":"192057"},{"date":"11:03 26/07","title":"Mourinho gi\u1ee5c l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o M.U mua g\u1ea5p sao tuy\u1ec3n Anh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/20/mourinho-giuc-mu-mua-maguire.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Mourinho gi\u1ee5c l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o M.U mua Maguire. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1t m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ni\u1ec1m tin t\u1eeb HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>H\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 M.U c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1eeb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, khu v\u1ef1c trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Man United \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn HLV Jose Mourinho kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng. D\u00f9 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t nh\u01b0 Eric Bailly, Chris Smalling hay Phil Jones c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01b0a n\u00f3i nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb nh\u01b0 Marcos Rojo, Daley Blind hay c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00e8 n\u00e0y, M.U \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 Blind tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Ajax. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ebft, h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1ea5p v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00f3. Th\u1ee9 2, vi\u1ec7c n\u00e2ng cao chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u1edbi Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho gi\u1ee5c l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o MU mua Maguire h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Mourinho gi\u1ee5c l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o MU mua Maguire h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/Mourinho-giuc-lanh-dao-MU-mua-Maguire-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Mourinho kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c trung v\u1ec7 M.U</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng Mourinho kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 c\u1ee1 Blind. \u00d4ng mu\u1ed1n M.U t\u1eadu h\u1eb3n m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nMourinho mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ngay Maguire</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau m\u00e0 M.U nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7, c\u00f3 c\u00e1i t\u00ean Harry Maguire. T\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, d\u00f9 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn c\u00f9ng \u0110T Anh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ea7y ch\u1eefng ch\u1ea1c. Ai c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec3 Gary Cahill d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho Maguire c\u1ee7a HLV Southgate l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Maguire DT Anh\" title=\"Maguire DT Anh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/Maguire-DT-Anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Mourinho gi\u1ee5c l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o M.U mua Maguire</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 gi\u1edd, \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a Southgate l\u00e0 Mourinho t\u00ednh lo\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t trong c\u00e1c trung v\u1ec7 hi\u1ec7n c\u00f3 c\u1ee7a M.U \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y ch\u1ed7 cho Maguire. Mourinho gi\u1ee5c l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o M.U mua Maguire l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd The Sun \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 World Cup 2018, \u201cNg\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t\u201d \u0111\u00e3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a Leicester City sau nh\u1eefng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Premier League 2 m\u00f9a qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p Leicester c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f2i 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Maguire, Mourinho tin r\u1eb1ng c\u0169ng l\u00e0 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng. Ph\u00f3 ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Ed Woodward \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng x\u00fac ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ec3 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 di\u1ec5n ra nhanh ch\u00f3ng. N\u1ebfu c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Maguire v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 tr\u00ean, M.U s\u1ebd bi\u1ebfn anh tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a Kyle Walker t\u1eeb Tottenham t\u1edbi Man City gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/tiet-lo-mu-va-real-tu-choi-mua-malcom-180-192001.html\">Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9: MU v\u00e0 Real t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i mua Malcom</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-muon-mua-bailey-thay-willian-172-191982.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! C\u00e1i t\u00ean Chelsea s\u1ebd mang v\u1ec1 n\u1ebfu b\u00e1n Willian cho M.U</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-muon-mu-co-them-2-tan-binh-172-191944.html\">Mourinho kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/3-thuong-vu-co-the-se-no-tai-man-united-trong-nhung-ngay-toi-187-191935.html\">3 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd n\u1ed5 t\u1ea1i Man United trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cuc-nong-mourinho-noi-dien-muon-tong-khu-martial-cang-nhanh-cang-tot-172-192038.html\">C\u1ef0C N\u00d3NG: Mourinho n\u1ed5i \u0111i\u00ean, mu\u1ed1n t\u1ed1ng kh\u1ee9 Martial c\u00e0ng nhanh c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1644","checkdouble":"192058"},{"date":"11:45 26/07","title":"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Bayern chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao tr\u1ebb Canada v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/chinh-thuc-bayern-chieu-mo-sao-tre-canada-voi-gia-ky-luc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sao tr\u1ebb 17 tu\u1ed5i Alphonso Davies \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gia nh\u1eadp Bayern Munich v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf gi\u1ea3i MLS.</h2><h2>Bayern chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Alphonso Davies\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Bayern chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Davies v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Bayern chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Davies v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/CHINH-THUC-Bayern-chieu-mo-Davies-voi-gia-ky-luc-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Bayern chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Davies v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 13.5 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u00f4la</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bayern \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a sao tr\u1ebb Alphonso Davies v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng 13.5 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u00f4la. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i MLS. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Jozy Alidore c\u1ee7a New York Red Bulls khi Villarreal \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd chi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed 10 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u00f4la v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2008.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu Davies th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t th\u00ec ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1ebd t\u0103ng l\u00ean 21.5 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u00f4la. Ph\u00eda Vancouver Whitecaps c\u0169ng k\u00e8m th\u00eam \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n y\u00eau c\u1ea7u Bayern ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 15% ti\u1ec1n ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u1ebfu b\u00e1n Davies trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nDavies s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 18 v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 11 v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gia nh\u1eadp Bayern v\u00e0o k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng. Theo lu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a FIFA, Davies kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i cho Bayern Munich t\u1edbi khi \u0111\u1ee7 18 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, HLV Niko Kovac kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh sao tr\u1ebb n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ed9t Bayern s\u1edbm khi m\u00e0 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i MLS k\u1ebft th\u00fac tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 \u0111\u00f4ng m\u1edf c\u1eeda.</div>\r\n<h2>Kovac khen ng\u1ee3i Davies</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau khi Bayern ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a Alphonso Davies, HLV Niko Kovac cho bi\u1ebft:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t tr\u1ebb nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t t\u00e0i n\u0103ng. Nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a Davies v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y. Nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb t\u00e0i n\u0103ng nh\u01b0 Davies th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eaft. Th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a Davies v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 v\u1eeba ph\u1ea3i cho d\u00f9 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t t\u00e0i n\u0103ng. T\u00f4i tin l\u00e0 Davies s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u00e8n luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nSao tr\u1ebb Davies c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.<br>\r\n<em><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Bayern. L\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1eadu b\u00e9, b\u1ea1n lu\u00f4n m\u01a1 t\u1edbi kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y. B\u00e2y gi\u1edd th\u00ec gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c v\u1edbi t\u00f4i. Nh\u01b0ng b\u00e2y gi\u1edd, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0y\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Bayern Munich:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-juventus-20-bayern-munich-icc-2018-329-192048.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Juventus 2-0 Bayern Munich (ICC 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/bayern-munich-bo-ngo-kha-nang-nhuong-sao-cho-man-utd-172-192007.html\">Bayern Munich b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng sao cho Man Utd</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1643","checkdouble":"192061"},{"date":"11:59 26/07","title":"Malcom \u2013 Ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a cho s\u1ef1 linh ho\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a Barcelona","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/26/malcom-chia-khoa-cho-su-linh-hoat-cua-barcelona.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1eadt \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft AS Roma. Nh\u01b0ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, Barca s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Malcom nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh?\r\n</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Barca tr\u1ea3 \u0111\u0169a Roma th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a h\u00e8 theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Willian &ndash; m\u1ed9t winger b\u00e1m c\u00e1nh, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i l\u1ea1i \u0111em v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t inside forward &ndash; ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u00e1nh Malcom, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng Barca \u0111ang loay hoay v\u1edbi ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tin \u0111\u00e1ng m\u1eebng khi h\u1ecd qu\u00e1 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mua b\u00e1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi, trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh v\u1eabn c\u00f2n Ousmane Dembele.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng g\u1ea1t s\u1ef1 nghi ng\u1edd sang m\u1ed9t b\u00ean, th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf l\u00e0 Blaugrana c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 h\u1ecd mong mu\u1ed1n. V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda sao tr\u1ebb Malcom, anh c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian v\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, v\u00ec v\u1eady v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0y h\u1ea1 h\u1ed3i ph\u00e2n gi\u1ea3i. V\u00e0 khi \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 Malcom, c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi \u0111\u1eb7t ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y &ndash; anh s\u1ebd \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Barcelona?<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn Barca s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Malcom nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 1\" title=\"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn Barca s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Malcom nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/Goc-nhin-Barca-se-su-dung-Malcom-nhu-the-nao-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca \u0111\u00e3 n\u1eabng tay tr\u00ean Roma \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Malcom</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h2>Gi\u1eef nguy\u00ean s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 v\u1ed1n c\u00f3<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi m\u1ea5t Neymar v\u00e0 \u0111em v\u1ec1 Dembele, Ernesto Valverde \u0111\u00e3 xoay Barca t\u1eeb 4-3-3 sang 4-4-2 gi\u0103ng ngang, v\u1edbi Paulinho v\u00e0 Iniesta \u1edf 2 h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh. \u0110\u00e2y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou, gi\u00fap h\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap gi\u1ea3i qu\u1ed1c n\u1ed9i m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc. V\u00ec th\u1ebf sau khi Paulinho v\u00e0 Iniesta ra \u0111i, Malcom ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u1ebfp v\u00e0o ch\u00ednh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u00f2n khuy\u1ebft n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1eb7p ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a G\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 v\u1eabn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 Leo Messi &ndash; Luis Suarez, trong khi Coutinho v\u00e0 Malcom \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m 2 h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh. Ousmane Dembele, l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf anh kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p l\u00e0m m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 b\u00e1m bi\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh, n\u00ean c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i s\u1ebd l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o tay t\u00e2n binh 41 tri\u1ec7u euro. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t d\u00e0i, v\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xoay tua v\u1edbi s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn Barca s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Malcom nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"malcom\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/4/vuot-mat-arsenal-va-mu-chelsea-sap-no-bom-tan-44-trieu-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Malcom c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i trong s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-4-2</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h2>Quay l\u1ea1i 4-3-3<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, Barca c\u0169ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 si\u00eau t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd, 4-3-3 l\u1eebng danh. V\u1edbi s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 n\u00e0y, tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd s\u1ebd l\u00e0 Busquets, Rakitic v\u00e0 Coutinho, trong khi h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u1ed3m Messi &ndash; Suarez &ndash; Malcom. Dembele nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i, s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1edbi v\u00e0 ch\u1edd c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfp theo.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u00f9ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng r\u00ea d\u1eaft, Malcom s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i n\u01a1i h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i. Messi v\u1eabn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u00f2i n\u1ed5 tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng Barca, c\u00f2n Suarez s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng qu\u1ea5y ph\u00e1 trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0, Malcom c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng thay th\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Neymar tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y hay kh\u00f4ng?<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn Barca s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Malcom nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/1.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>B\u1ed9 ba MSM m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Barca</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h2>S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng 2 s\u1ed1 9 \u1ea3o<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5t \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Valverde \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u1edbi 2 s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-3-3 d\u00f9 v\u1eabn v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean. Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i, ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Dembele v\u00e0 tu\u1ed5i t\u00e1c c\u1ee7a Suarez \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a Valverde th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, sau c\u00f9ng ph\u1ea3i xoay v\u1ec1 4-4-2 gi\u0103ng ngang, m\u1ed9t s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec v\u1eady \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, \u00f4ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n n\u00e0y v\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf h\u1eb3n Luis Suarez. \u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Barca khi \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh 4-3-3, ho\u1eb7c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 coi l\u00e0 4-3-1-2 v\u1edbi c\u1eb7p ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o s\u1ed1 9 \u1ea3o si\u00eau t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 - Ousmane Dembele v\u00e0 Malcom. M\u1ed9t s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 r\u1ea5t m\u1edbi l\u1ea1 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng qu\u00e2n b\u00e0i th\u00edch h\u1ee3p, d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u1edf gi\u1ea3i T\u00e2y Ban Nha.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn Barca s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Malcom nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 4\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/2.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ho\u1eb7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ea3 2 sao tr\u1ebb trong vai tr\u00f2 s\u1ed1 9 \u1ea3o</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h2>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 m\u00e0 thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Barca c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng, khi \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 n\u1eafm trong tay nh\u1eefng l\u00e1 b\u00e0i tr\u1ebb trung, t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 th\u00edch h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, m\u1ea5u ch\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 th\u00e0nh b\u1ea1i s\u1ebd l\u00e0 Valverde t\u00ecm ra m\u1ed9t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt t\u1ed1i \u01b0u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t huy s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2, \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd t\u1ef1 do, tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i nh\u1ea5t \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n r\u1ef1c l\u1eeda v\u1ed1n c\u00f3.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean, Valverde \u0111\u00e3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00ec l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 qu\u00e1 ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c Messi. D\u00f9 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3, nh\u01b0ng Malcom ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng thay th\u1ebf El Pulga trong m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, \u0111\u1ec3 \u00e1t ch\u1ee7 b\u00e0i c\u1ee7a Barca \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i. M\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i d\u00e0i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t, d\u00f9 ra s\u00e2n v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt n\u00e0o, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i c\u0169ng l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u00fd \u0111\u1ed3 c\u1ee7a HLV. N\u00f3i n\u00f4m na, t\u00e2n binh 41 tri\u1ec7u euro c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng t\u1ea1i Camp Nou, \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn l\u1eddi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1p cho nghi ng\u1edd Barca s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Malcom nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o?</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-vu-malcom-toi-barca-180-191986.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-vu-malcom-toi-barca.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-vu-malcom-toi-barca-180-191986.html\">4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau v\u1ee5 Malcom t\u1edbi Barca</span><br>\r\nBarca mua Malcom th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 41 tri\u1ec7u euro, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua danh s\u00e1ch 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/goc-nhin-nhung-tro-lo-va-so-thich-chuyen-nhuong-cua-barca-180-191984.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/goc-nhin-nhung-tro-lo-va-so-thich-chuyen-nhuong-cua-barca.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/goc-nhin-nhung-tro-lo-va-so-thich-chuyen-nhuong-cua-barca-180-191984.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Nh\u1eefng tr\u00f2 l\u1ed1 v\u00e0 s\u1edf th\u00edch chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Barca</span><br>\r\n&ldquo;Vui m\u1eebng&rdquo; sau khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c s\u1edf h\u1eefu t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Malcom, nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 l\u1ebd ch\u00ednh c\u00e1c C\u0110V c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i ng\u00e1n ng\u1ea9m v\u1edbi phong c\u00e1ch chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ki\u1ec3u Barca trong v\u00e0i n\u0103m...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1642","checkdouble":"192062"},{"date":"07:15 26/07","title":"Chelsea ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Alvaro Morata","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/20/chelsea-chot-gia-ban-alvaro-morata.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea b\u00e1n Alvaro Morata v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 58 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Gianluca Di Marzio ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9. Hi\u1ec7n AC Milan v\u00e0 Juventus \u0111ang quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Alvaro Morata</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Alvaro Morata ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Chelsea. B\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb Real Madrid ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 11 b\u00e0n \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. Morata t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf Premier League.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea b\u00e1n Alvaro Morata n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 58 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea b\u00e1n Alvaro Morata n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 58 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/22/Chelsea-ban-Alvaro-Morata-neu-nhan-duoc-58-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Sarri kh\u00f4ng th\u00edch phong c\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Morata</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, anh c\u0169ng b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ngon \u0103n. Ch\u00ednh phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Chelsea ch\u1ec9 x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 5 \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, qua \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 Champions League m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Maurizio Sarri t\u1ea1i Chelsea \u0111ang khi\u1ebfn Morata \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 26 tu\u1ed5i. Morata c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u01b0a th\u00edch c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 58 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh, HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Morata v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-nang-gia-hoi-mua-sao-khung-juventus-len-53-trieu-bang-172-191762.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Higuain c\u1ee7a Juventus</span>, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Morata</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea b\u00e1n Alvaro Morata v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 58 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Gianluca Di Marzio ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9. Hi\u1ec7n AC Milan v\u00e0 Juventus \u0111ang quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea b\u00e1n Alvaro Morata n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 58 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea b\u00e1n Alvaro Morata n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 58 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/9/dortmund-len-tieng-vu-quan-tam-morata.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea b\u00e1n Morata n\u1ebfu thu v\u1ec1 58 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Gianluca Di Marzio, gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Milan, Leonardo, \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp b\u00ed m\u1eadt v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Morata v\u00e0o h\u00f4m th\u1ee9 4. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan \u0111ang r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ef1u h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a AC Milan, Luca Antonini, tin r\u1eb1ng Morata s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho AC Milan \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi: \u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Morata v\u00e0 AC Milan \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn nhau. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Morata ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi Milan h\u01a1n l\u00e0 Karim Benzema\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Morata c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng r\u1eddi Chelsea n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng n\u1eb1m trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a HLV Sarri, tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 khi HLV Conte v\u1eabn c\u00f2n t\u1ea1i v\u1ecb, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u1edf l\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1641","checkdouble":"192040"},{"date":"07:44 26/07","title":"MU b\u00e1n Marcos Rojo \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 trung v\u1ec7 kh\u1ee7ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/18/mu-ban-marcos-rojo-de-dua-ve-trung-ve-khung.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Marcos Rojo \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Harry Maguire ho\u1eb7c Toby Alderweireld, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Manchester Evening News \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">M.U s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Marcos Rojo</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, trung v\u1ec7 Marcos Rojo kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o M.U b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Trong nh\u1eefng l\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 B\u00e1n Rojo mua Maguire ho\u1eb7c Alderweireld h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 B\u00e1n Rojo mua Maguire ho\u1eb7c Alderweireld h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/18/mu-ban-marcos-rojo-de-dua-ve-trung-ve-khung.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>M.U c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u00e1n Marcos Rojo \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1990 l\u00fac n\u00e0y b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ed9t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. Eric Bailly l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a HLV Jose Mouirnho \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7, Rojo ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi Smalling, Jones v\u00e0 Lindelof cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao 28 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang g\u1eb7p b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i so v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i b\u1edfi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng dai d\u1eb3ng v\u00e0 phong \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 t\u1ed1t \u1edf World Cup 2018.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Marcos Rojo \u0111\u1ec3 mua trung v\u1ec7 m\u1edbi, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Manchester Evening News \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf mu\u1ed1n\u00a0thu v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb 12 \u0111\u1ebfn 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>M.U nh\u1eafm Maguire ho\u1eb7c Alderweireld n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u00f4ng tin MU mua Toby Alderweireld \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1eeb kh\u00e1 l\u00e2u, song Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111ang g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 b\u1edfi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 55 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 Tottenham y\u00eau c\u1ea7u. Theo Mirror, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1ed1i \u0111a 44 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alderweireld\" title=\"Alderweireld\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/12/chuyen-nhuong-mu-hot-nhat-ngay-2107.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Alderweireld l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a M.U</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chot-thoi-diem-tottenham-va-mu-trao-doi-bom-tan-172-191994.html\" target=\"_blank\"> M.U \u0111\u1ed5i Martial l\u1ea5y Alderweireld </span>c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 t\u1ed1t cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c b\u00ean. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf v\u00e0 Spurs c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 m\u1edbi th\u00ec Martial v\u00e0 Alderweireld c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Toby Alderweireld, M.U s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang Harry Maguire c\u1ee7a Leicester City. Ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eeba c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Leicester v\u00e0 c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t \u1edf World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u201cB\u1ea7y c\u00e1o\u201d nh\u1ea3 Maguire, M.U ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1t khao m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 kh\u1ee7ng \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1640","checkdouble":"192041"},{"date":"07:55 26/07","title":"Arsenal ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb Milan \"ch\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ea7u\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/24/arsenal-chinh-thuc-len-tieng-ve-kha-nang-bi-milan-chat-dau.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trang ch\u1ee7 CLB th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u01b0a ra th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o b\u00e1c b\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chia tay gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh Ivan Gazidis v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal m\u1ea5t l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o v\u1ec1 tay Milan?</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ivan Gazidis \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c tr\u00ean th\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea7ng Emirates t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2008 nay v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng quan tr\u1ecdng. Th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd d\u1ea5y l\u00ean v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng doanh nh\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nam Phi s\u1ebd chia tay Arsenal trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y sau c\u1ea3 th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 g\u1eafn b\u00f3.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">CLB \u0111ang khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c C\u0110V Ph\u00e1o Th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ee9ng ng\u1ed3i kh\u00f4ng y\u00ean ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 Milan, \u00f4ng l\u1edbn n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed5i ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i n\u1eafm quy\u1ec1n ng\u1eafn ng\u1ee7i c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Trung Qu\u1ed1c. \u00d4ng ch\u1ee7 c\u0169 Li Yonghong tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 ph\u00e1 s\u1ea3n v\u00e0 bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i g\u00e1n kho\u1ea3n n\u1ee3 cho t\u1eadp \u0111o\u00e0n Elliott Management gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"G\u0110\u0110H Ivan Gazidis \u1edf l\u1ea1i Arsenal ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng gia nh\u1eadp Milan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"G\u0110\u0110H Ivan Gazidis \u1edf l\u1ea1i Arsenal ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng gia nh\u1eadp Milan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/24/arsenal-chinh-thuc-len-tieng-ve-kha-nang-bi-milan-chat-dau.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>G\u0110\u0110H Ivan Gazidis \u1edf l\u1ea1i Arsenal ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng gia nh\u1eadp Milan</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, \u0111\u1ea1i gia r\u1edfm \u0111\u1eddi g\u1ed1c Hoa kia \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i vay \u0111\u1ebfn 341 tri\u1ec7u Euro v\u1edbi l\u00e3i su\u1ea5t 11,5% t\u1eeb ch\u00ednh t\u1eadp \u0111o\u00e0n Elliott Management \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 mua l\u1ea1i Milan t\u1eeb c\u1ef1u th\u1ee7 t\u01b0\u1edbng \u00dd Silvio Berlusconi trong n\u0103m 2016. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, Elliott Management \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n San Siro v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f4n nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 Paolo Scaroni l\u00ean l\u00e0m t\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch CLB.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ivan Gazidis ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u1edf l\u1ea1i Emirates</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Cu\u1ed9c thay m\u00e1u ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Milan \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c v\u1edbi Leonardo, c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 v\u00e0 n\u1eafm gi\u1eef c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Rossoneri nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u0169ng s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i m\u1eddi l\u1ea1i n\u1ed1t Umberto Gandini l\u00e0m gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh sau th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a Arseanal v\u1ec1 Ivan Gazidis.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Trang ch\u1ee7 CLB th\u00e0nh London d\u1eabn l\u1eddi ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Chips Keswick: \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u00fd th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n xoay quanh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Ivan Gazidis, gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Vi\u1ec7c \u00f4ng \u1ea5y nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng khi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cTuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i xin nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh \u00f4ng \u1ea5y ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i m\u1edbi n\u00e0o c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00f4ng khai chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 n\u00f3. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n cam k\u1ebft g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u00e0 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho Arsenal, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u0111ang c\u00f9ng t\u00e2n HLV Unai Emery v\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 \u1edf Singapore \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/unai-emery-cong-thuc-monchi-trong-giac-mo-tai-cau-truc-cua-arsenal-172-187023.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/25/unai-emery-cong-thuc-monchi-trong-giac-mo-tai-cau-truc-cua-arsenal.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/unai-emery-cong-thuc-monchi-trong-giac-mo-tai-cau-truc-cua-arsenal-172-187023.html\">Unai Emery: C\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c Monchi trong gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 t\u00e1i c\u1ea5u tr\u00fac c\u1ee7a Arsenal</span><br>\r\nT\u1ea1i sao l\u00e0 Unai Emery?  Nhi\u1ec1u C\u0110V Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ecfi th\u1ebf khi bi\u1ebft t\u00ean ng\u01b0\u1eddi k\u1ebf nhi\u1ec7m gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i Arsenal. Nh\u01b0ng Unai Emery l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean th\u00edch h\u1ee3p nh\u1ea5t trong b\u00e0i...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1639","checkdouble":"192042"},{"date":"08:00 26/07","title":"Chris Smalling mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng sau khi b\u1ecb b\u1ecf r\u01a1i \u1edf World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/23/chris-smalling-muon-chung-to-kha-nang-sau-khi-bi-bo-roi-o-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chris Smalling ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf thu v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Smalling quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, trung v\u1ec7 Chris Smalling l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Jose Mourinho s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh M.U, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t. Tuy nhi\u00ean, anh l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch \u0110T Anh d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chris Smalling ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chris Smalling ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/23/chris-smalling-muon-chung-to-kha-nang-sau-khi-bi-bo-roi-o-world-cup-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Smalling mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Gareth Southgate \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp Phil Jones ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Smalling, b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u1edf ch\u1ed7 m\u00f9a v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i Jones d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Smalling xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n m\u1ed7i tu\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChris Smalling ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf thu v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cBan \u0111\u1ea7u t\u00f4i kh\u00e1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn m\u00e0 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n tham d\u1ef1. Sau \u0111\u00f3 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1\u00a0g\u1eafng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ed5 \u00edch, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 du l\u1ecbch \u1edf Th\u00e1i Lan v\u00e0 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y ph\u00fat th\u00fa v\u1ecb \u1edf \u0111\u00f3\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cB\u00e2y gi\u1edd t\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i v\u00e0 sung s\u1ee9c, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ra s\u00e2n th\u1eadt nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p nh\u1eefng g\u00ec l\u00e0 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho M.U. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Smalling kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec7n M.U mua trung v\u1ec7 m\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M.U \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, Mouirnho mu\u1ed1n <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/trung-ve-khung-dang-tren-duong-cap-ben-old-trafford-172-191829.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU mua Harry Maguire c\u1ee7a Leicester </span>ho\u1eb7c Toby Alderweireld c\u1ee7a Tottenham, song Smalling kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Smalling toa sang thuong xuyen o mua giai nay\" title=\"Smalling t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/19/smalling-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Smalling kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 quen v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n h\u00e0ng n\u0103m, M.U lu\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean k\u1ebft v\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tin \u0111\u1ed3n, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho M.U, m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y c\u00e0ng l\u00e2u c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t. C\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tin \u0111\u1ed3n cho r\u1eb1ng t\u00f4i s\u1ebd r\u1eddi M.U \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, song t\u00f4i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi Old Trafford\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1638","checkdouble":"192044"},{"date":"08:28 26/07","title":"\u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n sao Juventus x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea quan t\u00e2m","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/chinh-thuc-cuu-sao-chelsea-tro-ve-anh-khoac-ao-tan-binh-premier-league.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea quan t\u00e2m Rugani c\u1ee7a Juventus. \u0110\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 tin \u0111\u1ed3n m\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00ednh ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn v\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft Rugani</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nK\u1ebft th\u00fac m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18, Chelsea ch\u1ec9 x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 5 t\u1ea1i Premier League v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n d\u1ef1 Champions League m\u00f9a k\u1ebf ti\u1ebfp. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap The Blues gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00fap FA, HLV Antonio Conte v\u1eabn b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Italia, Maurizio Sarri.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSarri \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00ean n\u1eafm quy\u1ec1n v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng thay \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1. H\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 t\u1ea1i Napoli l\u00e0 Jorginho l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00f4ng mang v\u1ec1 Chelsea v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 57 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Ch\u01b0a d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i \u1edf \u0111\u00f3, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia 59 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f2n mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng Gonzalo Higuain v\u00e0 Daniele Rugani.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea quan t\u00e2m Rugani c\u1ee7a Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea quan t\u00e2m Rugani c\u1ee7a Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/Chelsea-quan-tam-Rugani-cua-Juventus-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">HLV\u00a0Sarri mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 c\u00e1c tr\u00f2 c\u0169</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHiguain t\u1eebng l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c d\u01b0\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbng Sarri m\u00f9a 2015/16, \u0111\u1ea1t t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec9nh cao s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p v\u1edbi 38 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 42 tr\u1eadn tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng. C\u00f2n Rugani, ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh t\u1eeb l\u00f2 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o Empoli t\u1eebng h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c v\u1edbi nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n n\u00e0y t\u1ea1i CLB giai \u0111o\u1ea1n n\u0103m 2013 t\u1edbi 2015.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRugani \u0111ang c\u00f9ng Juventus tham d\u1ef1 tour du \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9. \u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a anh, Davide Torchia m\u1edbi x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn s\u1ef1 theo \u0111u\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a Chelsea d\u00f9 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"hau ve Rugani\" title=\"hau ve Rugani\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/chinh-thuc-cuu-sao-chelsea-tro-ve-anh-khoac-ao-tan-binh-premier-league.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Chelsea quan t\u00e2m Rugani c\u1ee7a Juventus</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cChelsea quan t\u00e2m Rugani l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1eadt\u201d, Torchia n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Radio Sportiva. \u201cNgo\u00e0i v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 gi\u00e1 c\u1ea3 c\u00f2n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n khi kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Juventus. Nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi Gonzalo Higuain l\u00e0 ri\u00eang bi\u1ec7t. M\u1ed7i th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 c\u00f3 chi ph\u00ed kh\u00e1c nhau v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh kh\u00e1c nhau.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mang l\u1ea1i cho Juventus nh\u1eefng ngu\u1ed3n l\u1ee3i kh\u00e1c nhau. C\u00f2n Rugani, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang r\u1ea5t b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh v\u00e0 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 Juventus. Rugani v\u1eabn \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb song c\u1eadu \u1ea5y t\u1eadp trung cao nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho CLB hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.\u201d<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thuc-hu-vu-chelsea-chi-45-trieu-bang-mua-trung-ve-cua-juventus-172-192036.html\">Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 v\u1ee5 Chelsea chi 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/muc-tieu-tri-gia-100-trieu-euro-cua-mu-muon-gia-nhap-chelsea-172-192026.html\">M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u euro c\u1ee7a MU mu\u1ed1n gia nh\u1eadp Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-dat-thoa-thuan-ca-nhan-voi-courtois-180-192010.html\">N\u00f3ng: Sao Chelsea \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/juventus-mua-kante-neu-mat-pjanic-vao-tay-man-city-172-191995.html\">V\u00ec Man City, Chelsea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t Kante v\u00e0o tay Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-muon-mua-bailey-thay-willian-172-191982.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! C\u00e1i t\u00ean Chelsea s\u1ebd mang v\u1ec1 n\u1ebfu b\u00e1n Willian cho M.U</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1637","checkdouble":"192045"},{"date":"08:29 26/07","title":"Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c: Nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Anh kho\u00e1c \u00e1o t\u00e2n binh Premier League","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/Chinh-thuc-Tien-dao-Andre-Schurrle-gia-nhap-Fulham-tu-Dortmund-hinh-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Fulham ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 28 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c Andre Schurrle t\u1eeb Dortmund theo m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n hai n\u0103m.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh Premier League 2018/19 \u0111ang g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 khi b\u00f3ng c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u0103n trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecbu k\u00e9m c\u1ea1nh Wolverhampton, Fulham c\u0169ng \u0111ang g\u00e2y n\u00e1o lo\u1ea1n phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u0103m nay v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 Jean Michael Seri \u2013 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng Arsenal, Chelsea hay Barcelona theo \u0111u\u1ed5i.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Andre Schurrle gia nh\u1eadp Fulham t\u1eeb Dortmund h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Andre Schurrle gia nh\u1eadp Fulham t\u1eeb Dortmund h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/Chinh-thuc-Tien-dao-Andre-Schurrle-gia-nhap-Fulham-tu-Dortmund-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Andre Schurrle gia nh\u1eadp Fulham t\u1eeb Dortmund theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n trong hai n\u0103m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecbu d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y, CLB T\u00e2y London m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3n th\u00eam m\u1ed9t t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 ti\u1ebfng kh\u00e1c, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed h\u1eb3n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup b\u1ed1n n\u0103m v\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Andre Schurrle ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gia nh\u1eadp Fulham t\u1eeb Dortmund theo m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n hai n\u0103m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, ng\u00f4i sao 28 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1ed1n c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng l\u1ea1 g\u00ec b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh khi t\u1eebng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian hai m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1eeb 2013-2015 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Chelsea, c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t CLB T\u00e2y London kh\u00e1c. Anh th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng quang ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League trong n\u0103m 2015.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3, Schurrle ra \u0111i h\u1ed3i h\u01b0\u01a1ng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o nh\u1eefng Wolfsburg r\u1ed3i Dortmund nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecdn Fulham \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ee9u v\u00e3n s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. Kho\u00e1c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 14 quen thu\u1ed9c \u1edf Craven Cottage, nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2014 ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u trong ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cFulham l\u00e0 CLB \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 t\u00f4i, \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u00f4i h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c tr\u00e2n tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, t\u00ecnh y\u00eau v\u1edbi phong c\u00e1ch b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o v\u1edbi Fulham. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, t\u00f4i v\u1eabn s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n h\u1eefu \u00edch n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e2y.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-hang-hot-ligue-1-cap-ben-ngoai-hang-anh-172-191053.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/chinh-thuc-hang-hot-ligue-1-cap-ben-ngoai-hang-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-hang-hot-ligue-1-cap-ben-ngoai-hang-anh-172-191053.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: H\u00e0ng hot Ligue 1 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh</span><br>\r\nJean Michael Seri k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Fulham, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u00fa s\u1ed1c r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u1edbi NHM b\u1edfi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1636","checkdouble":"192047"},{"date":"08:13 26/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 26/07: T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Martial g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/22/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-2607-tuong-lai-martial-gan-nhu-da-duoc-xac-dinh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 26/07.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Martial g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 2607 T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Martial \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 2607 T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Martial \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/14/Diem-tin-bong-da-sang-2607-Tuong-lai-Martial-duoc-xac-dinh-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Martial s\u1eafp r\u1eddi M.U v\u00ec m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi Mourinho</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng MU b\u00e1n Anthony Martial l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao, HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111ang r\u1ea5t t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y r\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i b\u1ea3n doanh c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng b\u1ea1n g\u00e1i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00f3n c\u1eadu con trai s\u1eafp sinh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Sergej Milinkovic-Savic \u01b0u ti\u00ean Chelsea h\u01a1n l\u00e0 M.U</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italia, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Sergej Milinkovic-Savic c\u1ee7a Lazio \u01b0u ti\u00ean Chelsea h\u01a1n l\u00e0 M.U trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p r\u1eddi Lazio. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Serbia mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV Sarri.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Unai Emery tin Ozil s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd</h2>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mesut Ozil \u0111ang g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u00e1p l\u1ef1c sau quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chia tay \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c, song HLV Unai Emery tin r\u1eb1ng ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1988 s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chris Smalling mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng sau khi b\u1ecb b\u1ecf r\u01a1i \u1edf World Cup 2018</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chris Smalling ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf thu v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chris-smalling-muon-chung-to-kha-nang-sau-khi-bi-bo-roi-o-world-cup-2018-172-192044.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/23/chris-smalling-muon-chung-to-kha-nang-sau-khi-bi-bo-roi-o-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chris-smalling-muon-chung-to-kha-nang-sau-khi-bi-bo-roi-o-world-cup-2018-172-192044.html\">Chris Smalling mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng sau khi b\u1ecb b\u1ecf r\u01a1i \u1edf World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\nChris Smalling ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf thu v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>MU b\u00e1n Marcos Rojo \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 trung v\u1ec7 kh\u1ee7ng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Marcos Rojo \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Harry Maguire ho\u1eb7c Toby Alderweireld, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Manchester Evening News \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Alvaro Morata</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Morata\" title=\"Morata\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/22/Chelsea-ban-Alvaro-Morata-neu-nhan-duoc-58-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea s\u1eafp b\u00e1n Morata v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 58 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea b\u00e1n Alvaro Morata v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 58 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Gianluca Di Marzio ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9. Hi\u1ec7n AC Milan v\u00e0 Juventus \u0111ang quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>John Stones k\u1ecbp \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">John Stones t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng Man City s\u1edbm h\u01a1n d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh v\u1edbi Chelsea.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>H\u00e0ng hot Golovin t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Monaco mua Aleksandr Golovin th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u euro, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Ph\u00f3 ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Vadim Vasilyev c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng C\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Chelsea h\u1ecfi mua Rugani</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arsenal chi dam mua Rugani\" title=\"Arsenal chi \u0111\u1eadm mua Rugani\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/21/Chelsea-mua-Daniele-Rugani-voi-gia-35-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua mua Rugani</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua Daniele Rugani, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Davide Torchia c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 24 tu\u1ed5i x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Juventus \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thuc-hu-vu-chelsea-chi-45-trieu-bang-mua-trung-ve-cua-juventus-172-192036.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/7/17/thuc-hu-vu-chelsea-chi-45-trieu-bang-mua-trung-ve-cua-juventus.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thuc-hu-vu-chelsea-chi-45-trieu-bang-mua-trung-ve-cua-juventus-172-192036.html\">Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 v\u1ee5 Chelsea chi 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Juventus</span><br>\r\nChelsea \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua Daniele Rugani, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Davide Torchia c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 24 tu\u1ed5i x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Juventus \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1635","checkdouble":"192049"}]}